{"tid":2090240,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"認真討論，香港有多過一層樓嘅你有咩部署?","createTime":"2020-07-02T05:15:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T13:02:53.000Z","uid":28938,"like":28,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f491ae93450d919efba7cc97d9b28bf45e9c2552","tid":2090240,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:15:55.000Z","msg":"唔計自住，暫時有3個物業係手，夾埋仲有18m按揭未供完，不過憑租金已經每個月基本上打和，唔太擔心。<br />\n<br />\n呢個星期同老婆討論過未來部署：<br />\n<br />\n1. 幾層樓都繼續出住租先，但有好價會放售，底線係自住樓點都唔放。<br />\n2. 開始搵海外Agent睇下英國同澳洲樓，慢慢資產轉移，進可攻退可守。<br />\n3. 每個月收入用10%捐出去做善事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，幫多D社會有需要既人。"},{"pid":"f47e2c2deaffb8600c7a551b8779643c87310ca1","tid":2090240,"uid":137493,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875073ad3a1ae7be17d40446df6e3984fb660171","tid":2090240,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:19:06.000Z","msg":"留低收租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9529faf30d229505ccdb5aac1ef8594eae93a452","tid":2090240,"uid":19004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:20:29.000Z","msg":"香港agency 打理出租幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係幾想比屋企人打理"},{"pid":"a486012c24ac5c56c7a205710ea90304e8268169","tid":2090240,"uid":232091,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:20:32.000Z","msg":"得一層自住打算租出去走佬"},{"pid":"26f962525e166e020429931d0c780d59f1af0681","tid":2090240,"uid":28938,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f47e2c2deaffb8600c7a551b8779643c87310ca1","tid":2090240,"uid":137493,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:23:30.000Z","msg":"AA問多，實客好少"},{"pid":"039b18ab3623